messages.content: ComfyUI-Paint-by-Example is a custom node that implements the Paint-by-Example functionality, which is based on its corresponding implementation on the huggingface pipeline.
To install ComfyUI-Paint-by-Example, you need to copy the repo to your `./custom_nodes` directory in your comfyui workplace and install the used package in the nodes.py file.
Is there a demonstration available for ComfyUI-Paint-by-Example?
Yes, there is a demonstration available for ComfyUI-Paint-by-Example. You can view it by looking at the provided demo link or by viewing the demo.png file.
